    Scope and Contents
A student report entitled "Survey to Determine Contemporary Community Standards Existing in the  City of Springfield, Illinois and SSU during the winter of 1970-71" and to Determine the Feasibility of the Phrase, 'Contemporary Community Standards as a  Guideline for Censorship.' By George M. Pica &amp; Anne Goldfield.  Report includes survey data, raw survey questionnaires and test materials to determine attitudes toward pornography and censorship in the Springfield area.  
  
